{
  "text": "Initial studies of SC-FC correspondence [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] show that there is a relationship between these two entities via linear [CITATION_5] ) as well as more complex methods [CITATION_6] . However, there remains a gap in our understanding of how the two measures are related at the individual level.",
